fields.value: 1970 census fourth count school district data tapes

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This collection of data is a recompilation of the 1970 Census Fourth Count Population data, providing data tables for each school district in the country with 300 or more students.

The data contain half of the tables contained in the original tapes, including all tables requested by several dozen education planners consulted in the design phases.
